	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literę ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italia</placeName> ad me allatae sunt, quibus certe mihi significatur a nostris magnam cladem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispanensi</placeName> exercitui in <placeName ref="l150">Ferrariensi</placeName> ducatu esse illatam, et quanquam, quomodo res gesta sit, nondum per particulas intellexerim, tamen, quia hoc constat paulo minus duobus millis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispanorum</placeName> nullis nostris amissis cecidisse, id significare tibi volui.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu, si quid aliunde novi habeas, si scripseris, erit mihi gratissimum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Noster exercitus in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gallia</placeName> ad <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2235">Caletes</placeName> oppugnandos profectus est; sed magnitudo frigoris, quae etiam in regione illa vehementior est, me quicquam ex illa expeditione magni sperare vetat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quicquid erit, vos brevi intelligetis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">9a. ianuarii 1557 nostra computatione.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8183">Sanlaurent[ianus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo theologo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Henrico Bullingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="remark">[Darunter von anderer Hand:]</note>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">An herren <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495">Heinrich Bullinger</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
